<span><p>With PayPal, you can send payment quickly and securely online. Through PayPal, you can pay with credit card, debit card, or bank account balance. Once your order is submitted, you will be redirected to PayPal's site where you could make the payment.</p><br>
<p>For security we use Paypal and online real-time payment gateway which is one of the leading online payment processing companies in the world. All transactions take place in a secure environment (SSL), and we are not given any of your credit card details, simply a confirmation is given from Paypal that your payment has been authorized.</p><br>
Our PayPal Account is: <a href="mailto:paypal@joybuy.co.uk">pay@joybuy.co.uk</a> .
